item.title: About
item.description: Computer Engineer - Cat? Hi, I’m Tucker. I’m from south central Pennsylvania, where I went to high school in Spring Grove and was the section leader of the drumline and earned the name Tuckles. Recently I graduated from Elizabethtown College with a B.S. in Computer Engineering. Now I’ve moved to Lexington Park and work with NAVAIR. Hobbies Various electronics and programming projects Drawing and Photography Learning C++, Rust, and graphics programming Learning electric guitar and bass Interests Jennie PC Gaming (Starcraft, GTA, League of Legends, CIV VI) Music Cars, driving
